{"tid":1865150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】 孫春蘭:以戰時狀態落實各防控措施","createTime":"2020-02-06T04:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T04:49:53.000Z","uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d396727a2b9e5ee61c8a85d69124ff4749912521","tid":1865150,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:32:01.000Z","msg":"國務院副總理孫春蘭強調，要以戰時狀態落實落細各項防控措施。<br />\n<br />\n孫春蘭上午在武漢出席疫情會議時指出，各級領導幹部要把疫情防控作為當前最重要，堅決履行好屬地責任，堅決杜絕形式主義官僚主義，設立24小時值班制度，不能當逃兵，否則就會被永遠釘在歷史的恥辱柱上。<br />\n<br />\n她續稱，大家要心無旁騖、爭分奪秒，全力以赴解決措施不精確、落實不到位的問題，全力以赴保障人民群眾生命安全和身體健康，堅決打贏疫情防控阻擊戰。<br />\n<br />\n孫春蘭又表示，武漢市要舉全市之力，入戶上門排查，測體溫、詢問密切接觸者，全面落實轄區、行業部門、單位、個人責任，強化網格化管理，要不落一戶、不漏一人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2371742/%E5%AD%AB%E6%98%A5%E8%98%AD%3A%E4%BB%A5%E6%88%B0%E6%99%82%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B%E8%90%BD%E5%AF%A6%E5%90%84%E9%98%B2%E6%8E%A7%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2371742%2F%25E5%25AD%25AB%25E6%2598%25A5%25E8%2598%25AD%253A%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%258B%2580%25E6%2585%258B%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2590%2584%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=7ae5e0e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2371742/%E5%AD%AB%E6%98%A5%E8%98%AD%3A%E4%BB%A5%E6%88%B0%E6%99%82%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B%E8%90%BD%E5%AF%A6%E5%90%84%E9%98%B2%E6%8E%A7%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD</a>"},{"pid":"0018dea937c5e6757b69a08541ea30a6ce9e5750","tid":1865150,"uid":61967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"可控可防"},{"pid":"0daee3bf6639bac1a6e4a53320f3b235f3d35cab","tid":1865150,"uid":182875,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"完全唔知佢講乜9"},{"pid":"69608872de779e7a714206f31a28caaf3d8cb70b","tid":1865150,"uid":90328,"like":0,"di